id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ς \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. βρεσβ ύτερο ς\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>🕎\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">ΑΤΤΙΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΒΡΕΒ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΥΤΕΡΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>Σ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. βρεσβ ύτερο ς\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Brugnone and photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"3\">3: \u003Cspan>Brugnone: βρ&lt;ε&gt;σβ; lapis: βρϲβ, and since elsewhere lunate sigma is quadrate while epsilon is lunate, a weakly incised epsilon and omitted sigma seems more likely\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Attinis, (the) elder\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Presbuteros with initial B is also attested in \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003631\" target=\"_blank\">ISic003631\u003C/a> (Siracusa). The inscription is for a member of the council of elders within the local jewish community. The form Attinis is not otherwise documented. A second inscription was found in the same area by chance in 1948 this one (so Bonomi p.199), but is now lost and no details seem to be preserved, except that it consisted of four lines. \u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1996.0808 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 56.1081 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 52.0908 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 46.1245 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 15.0599 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1958.0563 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1.653b \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000582\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000582\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bonomi 1964 200 fig.35 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002127\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002127\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Noy 1993 no.157 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 2002 297-298 no.3 fig.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002118\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002118\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Crudely incised / scratched letters, Alpha with downard left-sloping bar, eyes of the beta are not closed, epsilon is lunate, sigma is lunate but with straight lines.\u003C/p> Line 2-5  40-70  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[260,263,266,269,272,275,278,281],{"id":261,"html":262},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>🕎 \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">Ἀττίν-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ις\u003C/span>\u003C/span> βρε&lt;σ&gt;β-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ύτερο-\u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ς \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. βρεσβ ύτερο ς\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>🕎\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">ΑΤΤΙΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΒΡΕΒ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΥΤΕΡΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>Σ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. βρεσβ ύτερο ς\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":264,"html":265},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>",{"id":267,"html":268},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Brugnone and photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"3\">3: \u003Cspan>Brugnone: βρ&lt;ε&gt;σβ; lapis: βρϲβ, and since elsewhere lunate sigma is quadrate while epsilon is lunate, a weakly incised epsilon and omitted sigma seems more likely\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":270,"html":271},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Attinis, (the) elder\u003C/p>  ",{"id":273,"html":274},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Presbuteros with initial B is also attested in \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003631\" target=\"_blank\">ISic003631\u003C/a> (Siracusa). The inscription is for a member of the council of elders within the local jewish community. The form Attinis is not otherwise documented. A second inscription was found in the same area by chance in 1948 this one (so Bonomi p.199), but is now lost and no details seem to be preserved, except that it consisted of four lines. \u003C/p>  ",{"id":276,"html":277},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1996.0808 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 56.1081 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 52.0908 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 46.1245 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 15.0599 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1958.0563 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1.653b \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000582\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000582\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bonomi 1964 200 fig.35 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002127\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002127\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Noy 1993 no.157 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 2002 297-298 no.3 fig.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002118\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002118\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":279,"html":280},"handnote","\u003Cp>Crudely incised / scratched letters, Alpha with downard left-sloping bar, eyes of the beta are not closed, epsilon is lunate, sigma is lunate but with straight lines.\u003C/p> Line 2-5  40-70  Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":282,"html":283},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[285,287,290,291],{"html":286},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\u003C/a>",{"id":288,"lang":131,"html":289},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>🕎 \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">Ἀττίν-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ις\u003C/span>\u003C/span> βρε&lt;σ&gt;β-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ύτερο-\u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ς \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. βρεσβ ύτερο ς\u003C/p>",{"html":286},{"id":292,"lang":131,"html":293},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>🕎\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀττίν\n                    ις\">ΑΤΤΙΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΒΡΕΒ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΥΤΕΡΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>Σ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.3 reg., orig. βρεσβ ύτερο ς\u003C/p>",[],[296],{"html":62},"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u003CteiHeader>\n        \u003CfileDesc>\n            \u003CtitleStmt>\n                \u003Ctitle>Funerary inscription of Attinis\u003C/title>\n                \u003Ceditor ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/editor>\n                \u003Cprincipal ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n\t   \u003Cfunder>\u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JCu\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728\">James Cummings\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>conversion to EpiDoc\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n\t    \u003CrespStmt>\n     \t       \u003Cname xml:id=\"SS\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569\">Simona Stoyanova\u003C/name>\n     \t       \u003Cresp>standardisation of template and tidying up encoding\u003C/resp>\n \t   \u003C/respStmt>\n            \u003C/titleStmt>\n            \u003CpublicationStmt>\n                \u003Cauthority>I.Sicily\u003C/authority>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"filename\">ISic001416\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"TM\">494019\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDR\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDH\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDCS\">38000220\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\">178081\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"URI\">http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001416\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"DOI\" when=\"2020-12-22\">10.5281/zenodo.4385910\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cavailability>\n                    \u003Clicence target=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.\u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Gela\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"museum\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/010\">Museo Archeologico Regionale di Gela\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003Cidno type=\"inventory\">9361\u003C/idno>\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\u003Cp>An irregular plaque of 'pietra arenaria', of irregular shape, broken into three joining fragments, with a section missing from the lower edge; the text is complete.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.sandstone\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/75.html\">sandstone\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.plaque\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259\">plaque\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\u003C!--Brugnone-->\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">72\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">42\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">6\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.fragments.contiguous\"/>\n\t\t    \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\u003Cp>Text over four lines to fit the width of the stone, below a menorah\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.complete\"/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003Cp>Crudely incised / scratched letters, Alpha with downard left-sloping bar, eyes of the beta are not closed, epsilon is lunate, sigma is lunate but with straight lines.\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line5\">Line 2-5\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\">40-70\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462423\">Philosophiana\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003Coffset>near\n                                    \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2524200\">Mazzarino\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003C/offset>\n                            \t\u003Cgeo>37.30188, 14.20959\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0401\" notAfter-custom=\"0500\" evidence=\"lettering textual-context\">5th century CE (so Brugnone)\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\" notBefore=\"1954\" notAfter=\"1961\">Found in contrada Fontanazzi (during excavations of 1954 / 1961), in the eastern part of the Sofiana cemetery, re-use in a boundary wall between two lots of the cemetery\u003Cgeo>37.3185981,14.3024473\u003C/geo>\u003C/provenance>\u003C!-- location of the eastern necropolis at Sofiana -->\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">none\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>                    \n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n             \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n             \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                     \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                 \u003C/xi:fallback>\n             \u003C/xi:include>\n\t  \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     \u003Cxi:fallback>\n\t       \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n\t     \u003C/xi:fallback>\n\t   \u003C/xi:include>\n         \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-22\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-03-12\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised from publication\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\u003Csurface/>\u003C!-- \n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001416_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001416.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\" source=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cg ref=\"#menorah\">&#x1f54e;\u003C/g>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Ἀττίν\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>ις\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cchoice>\u003Corig>βρε\u003Csupplied reason=\"omitted\">σ\u003C/supplied>β\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\" break=\"no\"/>ύτερο\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\" break=\"no\"/>ς\u003C/orig>\u003Creg>πρεσβύτερος\u003C/reg>\u003C/choice>\n               \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text after Brugnone and photograph\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"3\">\u003Cnote>Brugnone: βρ&lt;ε&gt;σβ; lapis: βρϲβ, and since elsewhere lunate sigma is quadrate while epsilon is lunate, a weakly incised epsilon and omitted sigma seems more likely\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Attinis, (the) elder\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Presbuteros with initial B is also attested in \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003631\">ISic003631\u003C/ref> (Siracusa). The inscription is for a member of the council of elders within the local jewish community. The form Attinis is not otherwise documented. A second inscription was found in the same area by chance in 1948 this one (so Bonomi p.199), but is now lost and no details seem to be preserved, except that it consisted of  four lines.\n                    \u003C!--epitaph of a member of the council of the elders, one Attinis (presbuteros). Attinis is an otherwise undocumented name, which Curbera concludes might be from Attinos or Attinas in a syncopated from from Attinios, a common Egyptian formation. C notes 'the scarcity of Latin names among Sicilian Jews'-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1996.0808\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>56.1081\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>52.0908\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>46.1245\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>15.0599\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"BE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1958.0563\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/77P5MNIR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIJ\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1.653b\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ACIZXQF2\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000582\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000582\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Noy\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1993\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>no.157\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/IBA4JMAN\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Bonomi\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1964\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>200 fig.35\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/BBEDUUG3\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002127\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002127\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Brugnone\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2002\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>297-298 no.3 fig.4\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/I6XXZEB6\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002118\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002118\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
